{"tid":1858611,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[BuyAndShit已夠貨] 網購外科口罩集中討論111","createTime":"2020-02-02T21:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T08:31:58.000Z","uid":58416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"732e318be7692278785707c3ec7e066df209e005","tid":1858611,"uid":58416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T21:04:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>內容及資料僅供參考，投資涉及風險，口罩價格可升亦可跌，甚至變成亳無價值。旅客在決定是否購買有關口罩之前應先閱讀有關風險評估，以了解該建議發售之詳細資料，並應就本身的財務、其他狀況及需要，詳細考慮並決定購買有關口罩是否切合本身特定的需要，若有需要更應咨詢其他專業意見，方可作出有關購買決定。<br />\n忠告：親自買罩 咪俾錢炒狗</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家基本上得返日本Amazon有現貨賣，<br />\n所以唔好買太多，到時禁運就真係攬炒一鑊熟。<br />\n<br />\n問呢個得唔得嘅，最少睇曬前2/3個post嘅圖。<br />\n<br />\n做開團團長嘅，求下你，你開個tg,wts gp出嚟畀人join，夠數就關link。<br />\n<br />\n間間集運都爆，唔好再問邊間快啲邊間好用，根本就無人知。<br />\n<br />\n記得留意返集運公司對體積重收費同要求，隨時運費貴過口罩本身，重有拒收嘅風險存在。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>麻煩大家Amazon唔好再用殘體字 有得揀英文/日文</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"bc2eb88f6b688ae86dfba58a5e60029142f48032","tid":1858611,"uid":282298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T21:10:39.000Z","msg":"Hello anybody here?"},{"pid":"086e844411756469f15dad53c3016b04f36f08e5","tid":1858611,"uid":58416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc2eb88f6b688ae86dfba58a5e60029142f48032","tid":1858611,"uid":282298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T21:10:39.000Z","msg":"Hello anybody here?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T21:10:57.000Z","msg":"Hello"},{"pid":"48e9210e227824b86fc0a336924d3296dc7e7c31","tid":1858611,"uid":282298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T21:16:47.000Z","msg":"